{"tid":44120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(午餐肉)真的來了，巨型藍光柱劃破黑夜","createTime":"2016-12-18T04:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T06:02:02.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"099dbd7b18dcde9c3ad3900f9c135391441250a0","tid":44120,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161216/bknint-20161216213802249-1216_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161216%2Fbknint-20161216213802249-1216_17011_001.html&d=p0T6VhiWqbaOsJYg%2FGj8KUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f8cfc5fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161216/bknint-20161216213802249-1216_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=p0T6VhiWqbaOsJYg%2FGj8KUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=16828029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】西班牙有facebook群組近日瘋傳一條不明飛行物體（UFO）片段。從片中可見，烏雲密布的天空中，有一個疑為UFO的圓形物體，射出一道藍色的光柱，劃破天際。 <br />\n<br />\n片段拍攝的確實時間和地點不明，不少網民看畢片段後，大感驚訝，指該光柱由外星人的飛船發出，並即將離開地球。有網民質疑片段的真偽，亦有人指片段中的藍色光柱其實只是閃電而已。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/123209_f37a1b02bdc8664fb5fcbb7be182d966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F123209_f37a1b02bdc8664fb5fcbb7be182d966.jpg&h=925e5003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家屋企仲有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daafe283256ee9fbb06467bccd652c54df020b7","tid":44120,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，今次NASA點解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmo